The Jelly Belly Factory tour is a sweet way to spend an afternoon. You'll get to see the behind-the-scenes magic of jelly bean production and, of course, indulge in some delicious samples. Just a heads up, it's always a good idea to check the factory's official website or contact them directly for the most up-to-date information on tour timings and any special events. Have a great time on your jelly bean adventure!
